----------------------TASK-6---------------------------------------
TASK : General Automate Strapi Deployment with GitHub Actions + Terraform

CI Pipeline (Continuous Integration)
1)Builds the Strapi Docker image
2)Pushes the image to AWS ECR
3)Produces an image tag output used by CD pipeline

CD Pipeline (Continuous Deployment)
1)Accepts the image tag manually
2)Runs Terraform (init â†’ plan â†’ apply)
3)Provisions AWS Infrastructure
4)EC2 automatically pulls the correct tagged image from ECR
5)Runs Strapi container connected to RDS PostgreSQL

This establishes a full automated DevOps flow from code â†’ image â†’ infrastructure â†’ deployment.




